    Chunk handling vulnerability.
<li><a href="$(HOME)/security/2002/dsa-132">Apache-SSL</a> --
    Chunk handling vulnerability.
<li><a href="$(HOME)/security/2002/dsa-133">Apache-Perl</a> --
    Chunk handling vulnerability.
<li><a href="$(HOME)/security/2002/dsa-134">OpenSSH</a> --
    Remote vulnerability.
</ul>

